Let's begin!!

Rains are back. Go on a weekend getaway trip to Vikatgad-Peb fort, a part of the Matheran hill range and a popular destination among trekkers this weekend. Pass through deep ravines and cliffs which are enough to get your adrenaline soaring! Enjoy the spellbinding view from the top and have an unforgettable experience with us. Don't forget to get drenched in the beautiful waterfalls on the way.

Event organized by @things2doinmumbai & @luxortrails
Dates - 30th Jun'19 (Sunday)
For Queries, contact- Akansha (9764477894)
